source: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_050<tab><blip> Greetings, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. Thank you for agreeing to knock Thiuna into shape.
target: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_050<tab><biep> Registriere <var 29 EB02 /var>. <biep> Bringe Thiuna mit kräftigen Schlägen in Form!

source: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_100<tab><blip> Be kindly informed that your every action is currently being recorded. <buzz> Remember to smile.
target: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_100<tab><biep> Aufzeichnung der Taten von <var 29 EB02 /var> läuft<var 1D /var>... <biep> <biep> <biep>

source: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_150<tab><blip> Glory be to Allag. Long may she endure.
target: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_150<tab><biep> Ein Hoch auf das Allagische<var 1D /var>... Kaiser... <biiiep> <Zzzzzz>

source: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_160<tab><blip> Water and nodes do not mix. As a precautionary measure, I must maintain a safe distance from amaro.
target: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_160<tab><biep> Ich kann Amaros nicht leiden. Amaros sind bösartig und gefährlich!

source: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_200<tab><blip> Be advised that forced shutdowns may result in corrupted data. It is recommended that you perform regular backups.
target: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_200<tab><biep><var 1D /var>... <biiiep><var 1D /var>... Erzwungene Neustarts sind nur eingeschränkt zu empfehlen. Datensicherung ist zwingend erforderlich.
TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_250<tab><biep><var 1D /var>... Irgendwie scheint meine Datenverarbeitungsgeschwindigkeit eingeschränkt zu sein<var 1D /var>... <Zzzz><var 1D /var>...

source: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_350<tab><blip> All data pertaining to <var 29 EB02 /var> has been encrypted under the Protect protocol. <buzz> Your personal information is safe with me.
target: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_350<tab><biep><var 1D /var>... Alle Aufzeichnungen über <var 29 EB02 /var> wurden von Thiuna geschützt.
